         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Finance Plan To Report
Process Group: DC Manage Accounting and Control Data
Process: DC-010-160B CFIN CO Objects Mapping_R3</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-96F009E0-73B6-4106-AB8E-2EE60BCCD9DE" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Source Production &amp; Maintenance Order will be created as Internal Order in CFIN automatically. Source System can be ECC, IF or IP for R3.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
